# Brain Tumor AI Model

## Overview
This project focuses on building a machine learning model to detect brain tumors from data inputs. The goal is to demonstrate how AI can support healthcare diagnostics.

## What I Did
- Cleaned and preprocessed dataset
- Applied feature engineering techniques
- Trained machine learning models
- Evaluated performance using metrics

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn

## Results
The model successfully identified patterns in the dataset and demonstrated the potential of AI in medical analysis.

## Key Takeaways
- Importance of clean data
- Model evaluation is critical
- Real-world applications require ethical consideration
